Write a Python program that generates a random array of 10 numbers and calculates the mean and median of the array using NumPy functions.
-------------------------------------

import numpy as np

# Generate a random array of 10 numbers
random_array = np.random.rand(10)

# Calculate the mean and median using NumPy functions
mean_value = np.mean(random_array)
median_value = np.median(random_array)

# Display the results
print("Random Array:", random_array)
print("Mean:", mean_value)
print("Median:", median_value)
